normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定只係想搵多人頭夾份錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:18:42.000Z","msg":"其實上次同佢地食打邊爐放題已經好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為我唔食牛羊嗰啲，嗰陣佢地突登為左我整個爐係唔落牛羊肉，但其實佢地個個都好中意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驚再咁落去以後食飯都唔預我"},{"pid":"12449afe62e72905c7f9a0a397d3d97ed08f2805","tid":1857342,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c21690d290a4508207af1697b3c35f9cba6e5302","tid":1857342,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"P牌仔又做嘢，拉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"創台得罪你班cctai狗？"},{"pid":"07768032594b2a545d8fbaf975ab5c6826700a5e","tid":1857342,"uid":148497,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"39a1c879352fb859021345bb09f66a2159aa0837","tid":1857342,"uid":301809,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"5c5a848ec982746fd9fac8c3755639ba65e3f6ed","tid":1857342,"uid":148497,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:54:57.000Z","msg":"直接同佢講自己唔食魚生，問下轉去食其他好唔好，正常fd既都會去D大家都想既地方。如果對方話唔好，你要確定一下佢係唔係真係你朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定只係想搵多人頭夾份錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:18:42.000Z","msg":"其實上次同佢地食打邊爐放題已經好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為我唔食牛羊嗰啲，嗰陣佢地突登為左我整個爐係唔落牛羊肉，但其實佢地個個都好中意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驚再咁落去以後食飯都唔預我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:30:50.000Z","msg":"咁你又真係好似好多野唔食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢地都繼續約你，咁睇真係fd底黎。你或者檢討下自己點解哩樣唔食 o個樣唔食，不過咁大間店,唔會只得魚生既，即使真係得魚生，當係去傾下計囉，fd呢樣野得黎不易。<br />\n<br />\n當然你可以用下口術，講話&ldquo;我唔食魚生，去另外一到食好唔好，如果真係想去食魚生都唔緊要，我都可以陪你地嫁，咁大間店應該搵到我食既野（講哩句說話時，全程保持笑容）&ldquo;。<br />\n<br />\n對方聽到應該會明白你係明事理人，而且知道你唔食都願意陪佢地去，會有小小反省，同時又可以駁下轉唔轉到去另一到食。"},{"pid":"a5cbaa0ebc60f28fef2bb3ba11e4ca6c8e19de05","tid":1857342,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:31:10.000Z","msg":"你話你發左幾日燒同咳囉"},{"pid":"fe26c5b4302465e4a3712aa2b025a66be7ee63c1","tid":1857342,"uid":265153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:32:59.000Z","msg":"同佢地絕交啦 魚生都食？都唔知係咪人黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312027f09bce6289602c5e650c810253db0e6d2c","tid":1857342,"uid":75100,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:33:42.000Z","msg":"我同樓主你一樣，又係唔食生冷野+牛，次次有人約食飯都煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但你咁諗啦，食飯其次，同fd傾計先係重點，唔好諗蝕唔蝕，食自己中意既野就ok，至少日式放題你有大把選擇，好過打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a6740afde3df236af78903ea88b13e096b3981","tid":1857342,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:36:26.000Z","msg":"你話你去完支那啱啱返港囉"},{"pid":"4298f62911c7d53bcbeccec4834fb52389b46bb3","tid":1857342,"uid":44815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"我有朋友都係唔食魚生。佢每次都會叫個鍋，整熱d魚生食"},{"pid":"5abf8792c9918e5308d05a1afca638df0973de3e","tid":1857342,"uid":228894,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:52:55.000Z","msg":"雞翼，天婦羅，炒什菜，炸什菌，炸蠔，焗蠔，秋刀魚，鯖魚，牛柳粒，雞軟骨&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"bb4a231ab3d10ae88734f429bee1beeabcd5b32a","tid":1857342,"uid":301809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"07768032594b2a545d8fbaf975ab5c6826700a5e","tid":1857342,"uid":148497,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"39a1c879352fb859021345bb09f66a2159aa0837","tid":1857342,"uid":301809,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"5c5a848ec982746fd9fac8c3755639ba65e3f